<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٢٢١٤ - عَنْ مَعْمَرٍ , عَنِ الْكَلْبِيِّ ,<span class="c5"> فِي قَوْلِهِ تَعَالَى:</span> <span class="c3">{الْمُبَارَكَةِ مِنَ الشَّجَرَةِ}</span> <span class="c4">[القصص: ٣٠]</span> ,<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«شَجَرَةُ الْعَوْسَجِ»</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>